Build a man is a simple, console game and a variation of Hangman.

1. A random book title is going to be select from the text file.
2. The chosen book author is going to be read from another text file.
3. A player will have to guess the book title by guessing letters (similar to the Hangman game).
4. After the player guess the book title correctly they will be asked to deliver the name of the book's author.
5. To fully win the game you have guess both book from the Hangman game and give the author's name.

Additional notes:
1. Player can choose how many times he will be allowed to guess the letter.


